data.description: This townhome is surrounded by lush greenery, providing a peaceful environment. Boasting an immaculate floor plan, the property features two master suites, each with its own private bathroom and walk-in closet. One of the master suites also has access to a private balcony overlooking splendid gardens and a swimming pool. The first floor features an open-concept kitchen, living room, and dining room. The kitchen is charming, with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a garden window, and a chef's table. The living room has French doors that open to a screened-in patio, bringing the outdoors inside. Additionally, there are enclosed separate quarters with a third bedroom and a half bath. A third gated patio leads to a two-car carport. The community offers a splendid swimming pool and a covered patio that helps to make gatherings even more enjoyable. Throughout the gardens, a peaceful and woodsy atmosphere prevails with pine trees.
